:

1. *Dr* se veselim tvojem dolasku. (I'm looking forward to your arrival.)
2. *Dr*žim palčeve da će sve biti u redu. (I'm keeping my fingers crossed that everything will be alright.)
3. *Dr*žava je preuzela odgovornost za ovu krizu. (The state has taken responsibility for this crisis.)
4. *Dr*ago mi je da smo se videli. (It was nice seeing you.)
5. *Dr*žava je donela odluku o ovoj temi. (The state has made a decision on this topic.)